              <p class="description"> "food is excellent, absolutely delicious, best breakfast and pizza and the services are also good."</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card swiper-slide">
            <div class="image-content">
              <span class="overlay"></span>

              <div class="card-image">
                <img src="Images/sri-ram.jfif" alt="sisriram" class="card-img" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-content">
              <h2 class="name">Sid Sriram</h2>
